<p>I am using Joomla default users table and storing multiple types of user using  User Group, I want to allow user to store unique email by usergroup, currently Joomla users table doesn't allow to store same email id for different User Group.</p>  <p>For example : User Group 1)admin, 2)customer.</p>  <p>Then I want to add user with the email id "test@test.com" in both admin and customer group.</p>  <p>I am using Joomla's default component.</p>